# Visual System

## Colors
- Primary: #3B82F6
- Success: #22C55E
- Warning: #F59E0B
- Danger: #EF4444
- Background: #F5F7FB
- Card: #FFFFFF
- Border: #E5E7EB

## Spacing
- Use ONLY: 8px, 16px, 24px, 32px

## Radius
- Card: 12px
- Input: 8px

## Shadow
- Soft shadow only

## Typography
- Title: 24px bold
- Section: 18px semi-bold
- Body: 14px

## Rules
- Avoid clutter
- Keep UI clean and modern